  "text": "Analysis software. A novel image-analysis software (IwmUltrasonic; version 2.0; Ditect Co., Ltd., Tokyo, Japan) was developed based on an algorithm previously reported [CITATION_1] . This software analyzes the video files obtained with CEUS. Visible particles were used to draw accumulated color points revealing the distribution of capillary vessels. This software is able to simultaneously calculate the density of particles in the drawn figures, which is hypothesized to represent the capillary density of the lymph nodes.",
